<bibRefCitation author="Aurivillius" box="[151,346,846,871]" pageId="1" pageNumber="446" refString="Aurivillius, C. (1923) Coleopterorum Catalogus, pars 74, Cerambycidae: Lamiinae II. W. Junk, Berlin, 382 pp. [pp. 323 - 704] Bates, H. W. (1866) III. Contributions to an insect fauna of the Amazon Valley. Coleoptera: Longicornes. The Annals and Magazine of Natural History, Series 3, 17, 31 - 42." type="book chapter" year="1923">Aurivillius, 1923</bibRefCitation>
