<bibRefCitation author="Bates" box="[1108,1267,847,871]" pageId="1" pageNumber="446" refString="Bates, H. W. (1881 a) Biologia Centrali-Americana. Insecta, Coleoptera. Fol. 5. Published for the editors by R. H. Porter, London, 72 pp. [pp. 153 - 224]" type="book chapter" year="1881" yearSuffix="a">Bates (1881a)</bibRefCitation>
