<bibRefCitation author="Bates" box="[293,455,918,943]" pageId="1" pageNumber="446" refString="Bates, H. W. (1881 b) Notes on longicorn Coleoptera. Revision of the Aerenicides and Amphionychides of Tropical America. The Annals and Magazine of Natural History, Series 5, 8, 290 - 306." type="journal article" year="1881" yearSuffix="b">Bates (1881b)</bibRefCitation>
