<bibRefCitation author="Martins" box="[199,515,1026,1051]" pageId="1" pageNumber="446" refString="Martins, U. R. &amp; Galileo, M. H. M. (1991 a) Subdivisao do genero Lycidola Thomson, 1864 (Coleoptera, Cerambycidae, Lamiinae, Hemilophini). Revista Brasileira de Entomologia, 35 (3), 553 - 565." type="journal article" year="1991" yearSuffix="a">Martins &amp; Galileo (1991a)</bibRefCitation>
